？！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:03:32.000Z","msg":"Here is CC Tai"},{"pid":"442999dc1d64d6106c2320b3753d738698c6cdc5","tid":2162744,"uid":334406,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:06:09.000Z","msg":"不反對食貓狗 但點解要毆打佢 又唔見有人毆打隻牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"505c62a940a4f06c2e80d0681c4ccc8387c22012","tid":2162744,"uid":109543,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"586301230f1f0468795d2274ce8f9ea04e62a79a","tid":2162744,"uid":167928,"like":4,"dislike":16,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"22bc756f10e39279a22b47dd6b668a9384a4ace3","tid":2162744,"uid":246697,"like":17,"dislike":5,"score":12,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:30:47.000Z","msg":"又黎世界大戰<br />\n<br />\n豬牛羊禽vs貓狗<br />\n<br />\n植物都有生命<br />\n<br />\netc"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:35:04.000Z","msg":"已經有牛豬雞羊食 仲食貓狗 根本係缺乏文明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:11:12.000Z","msg":"雖然我都唔贊成食貓狗<br />\n但係你依句真係好撚柒偽善<br />\n牛豬雞羊同貓狗既分別再於你將感情放落d貓狗到<br />\n如果你咁撚大愛應該所有動物都唔應該食<br />\n因為你一樣係屠殺緊其他動物<br />\n而個分別只係因係你覺得貓狗可愛d,你覺得貓狗有靈性d<br />\n所以你對佢地有感情覺得佢地就唔算係家畜而係寵物"},{"pid":"55af58266404a83a25e82f2318f62c22ad3e103b","tid":2162744,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:12:56.000Z","msg":"基本上有讀中化都好易答到呢題<br />\n年年中化都有問咁滯"},{"pid":"0f8fee19c28fe9c7105b6f6d47118b41dacc0c71","tid":2162744,"uid":8308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:14:52.000Z","msg":"如果養黎食用 我覺得冇問題<br />\n但毆打虐待真係幾仆街下"},{"pid":"13a9c810ab386ab4dcfa9c651cb353fdce84897a","tid":2162744,"uid":2615,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"586301230f1f0468795d2274ce8f9ea04e62a79a","tid":2162744,"uid":167928,"like":4,"dislike":16,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"22bc756f10e39279a22b47dd6b668a9384a4ace3","tid":2162744,"uid":246697,"like":17,"dislike":5,"score":12,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:30:47.000Z","msg":"又黎世界大戰<b